border.description: A subtle border for use in components that require a less prominent border

alt.description: Alternative for the secondary content area of the app

strong.description: A stronger border for use in components that require a more prominent border

subtle.description: A subtle border for use in components that require a less prominent border

background.description:
Context Menus, use a specific component-level token: context-menu-backdrop-background
This is done so that Context Menus in Midnight theme have enough contrast against the background.

default.description: The background color for the Alert component on mobile. This is just background-base-low but does not have the same gradient theme colors.
The background color for the Coachmark component on mobile. This is just background-surface-highest but does not have the same gradient theme colors.
